{"ts": "2026-06-09T22:49:24.271344+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Unfortunately, the GitHub token available to me doesn't have write permissions to this repository, so I cannot push the fix directly. However, I've fully analyzed the issue and can describe exactly what needs to be changed.\n\n## Issue #1: Fix a Broken Documentation Link\n\n### Analysis\n\nIn `docs/intro.md`, the link to the getting-started page currently reads:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\nIn **Docusaurus**, internal documentation links should reference the **document ID** (as defined in the front matter), **not** the raw `.md` filename. Since `docs/getting-started.md` has `id: getting-started` in its front matter, the link should be `./getting-started` without the `.md` extension.\n\nWith the `.md` extension, Docusaurus may fail to resolve the link correctly, resulting in a broken navigation experience.\n\n### Required Change\n\nIn **`docs/intro.md`**, change the last line from:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started.md).\n```\n\nto:\n\n```markdown\nContinue to [Getting Started](./getting-started).\n```\n\nThis is a one-character fix — just remove `.md` from the link target.\n\n### Validation\n\nThe `scripts/validate_repo.py` script checks for required files and JS exports but does not inspect link syntax, so the fix won't break any existing validation. The change is purely scoped to the documentation link as requested in the issue.\n\n### Limitation\n\nI was unable to commit this change because the GitHub token lacks write access (all push attempts returned `403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`). A contributor with write access would need to apply this single-line fix.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 394, "prompt_tokens": 7575, "total_tokens": 7969, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 30, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 7296, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0004904106, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001476306, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00034278}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1781045356-iL3DGm58tB39EMUXQ9eu", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019eae93-67aa-7373-b764-0c89c9e061d3-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7575, "output_tokens": 394, "total_tokens": 7969, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 7296}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 30}}}}]}}}
